name: The Bachelor
overview: The series revolves around a single bachelor (deemed eligible) and a pool of romantic interests, which could include a potential wife for the bachelor. The conflicts in the series, both internal and external, stem from the elimination-style format of the show. Early in the season, the bachelor goes on large group dates with the women, with the majority of women eliminated during rose ceremonies. As the season progresses, women are also eliminated on one-on-one dates and on elimination two-on-one dates. The process culminates with hometown visits to the families of the final few women, overnight dates, should they choose to accept, at exotic locations with the final three women, and interaction with the bachelor's family with the final two women. In many cases, the bachelor proposes to his final selection.

seasons.name: Season 1
seasons.overview: The first season of The Bachelor Australia premiered on September 8, 2013. This season features 30-year-old Tim Robards, a Sydney chiropractor.

episodes.name: Episode 1
episodes.overview: Australia finally has a Bachelor to call their own. Meet Tim Robards, a chiropractor with a practice in Sydney, Tim is taking on the once-in-a-lifetime chance of searching for true love among 25 of Australia's most eligible bachelorettes.

episodes.name: Episode 2
episodes.overview: A select group of girls go on a date with Tim to a photo shoot for a national magazine. One bachelorette will be chosen by Tim to be whisked away to one of Australia's most beautiful coastal towns for the first single date of the series.

episodes.name: Episode 3
episodes.overview: As Tim slowly gets to know each of our Bachelorettes, he's selecting a few favourites to head up the coast and into the sand dunes for a date that has an exotic touch.

episodes.name: Episode 1
episodes.overview: Things are about to heat up: it's Bachelor season. Hearts will melt as 22 of Australia's most eligible ladies vie for Richie Strathan's attention as he returns in the hope of finding true love.

episodes.name: Episode 2
episodes.overview: One lucky Bachelorette is whisked away to a secluded beach by private chopper for the first single date of the season. The group date sees the bachelorettes embrace the 50s for a magazine photoshoot.

episodes.name: Episode 3
episodes.overview: Just how high will Richie go for love? How about going on a date suspended off a clifftop above crashing waves below? Later, the good times roll in a competitive group date with a twist.

episodes.name: Episode 4
episodes.overview: With a licence to thrill, Richie channels his inner James Bond as he takes one lucky bachelorette on a spectacular date to remember. Later, a Cinderella ball awaits the winner of a waltz dance-off.

episodes.name: Episode 5
episodes.overview: Like a scene out of Pretty Woman, the single date sees Richie and a lucky girl arrive at fashion designer Camilla's store in a limousine. Later on the group date 'Nobody puts Baby in the corner'.

episodes.name: Episode 6
episodes.overview: Richie and his date take to the skies aboard a helicopter en-route to an intimate dinner for two. Plus, the group date heads to the inaugural Bachelor Games - a sporting championship like no other.

episodes.name: Episode 7
episodes.overview: Richie takes one lucky lady to the seas tonight, hoping for a love story of Titanic proportions. Later, Richie invites the Bachelorettes to a garden party but will he even show up?

episodes.name: Episode 8
episodes.overview: One Bachelorette is flying high when she becomes the first to be chosen for a second single date. Later, Richie surprises the Bachelorette's with a date that will put their cooking skills to the test.

episodes.name: Episode 9
episodes.overview: Richie is hoping to take it up a notch as he takes his chosen lady for a high-octane jet-ski ride. Plus - is it possible to measure love? Richie puts his group dates up for a compatibility test.

episodes.name: Episode 10
episodes.overview: Richie takes the plunge on a steamy single date with one lucky Bachelorette. Plus, the eight remaining Bachelorettes battle it out in the first Bachelor Highland Games.

episodes.name: Episode 2
episodes.overview: Who has made the best first impression? Who will Matty choose for the first single date? Later, who will catch Matty’s eye on the group date.

episodes.name: Episode 3
episodes.overview: Who has made the best first impression? Who will Matty choose for the first single date? Later, who will catch Matty’s eye on the group date.

episodes.name: Episode 11
episodes.overview: Some bachelorettes are left reeling when Matty invites someone on a second single date. Later, one bachelorette's effort to impress backfires in spectacular fashion but will she be the next to leave?

episodes.name: Episode 12
episodes.overview: Matty takes a lucky bachelorette sky high on a luxurious single date. Will this see their romance reach new heights? Later, on the group date, the bachelorettes reveal what's holding them back in love.

episodes.name: Episode 13
episodes.overview: Matty is wanting to spend as much time as possible with the remaining six Bachelorettes before making the all-important decision of whose families he will visit.

episodes.name: Episode 14
episodes.overview: Matty travels the country to meet the friends and families of the final four bachelorettes. Will he survive the grilling from protective parents and friends and meet their expectations?

episodes.name: Episode 15
episodes.overview: After hometown visits, Matty’s feelings escalate for the remaining three women. With the finale around the corner, he can only choose two of these incredible women to meet his family.

episodes.name: Finale
episodes.overview: Two wonderful women are on their way and the time has come for Matty to make one of the hardest decisions of his life. With emotions and hearts on the line, who will Matty choose to be with forever?

episodes.name: Episode 2
episodes.overview: The first single date of the series sees one lucky Bachelorette join Bachelor, Nick on a secluded beach where he pulls out all the stops to impress. Later, the claws come out on a group date.

episodes.name: Episode 3
episodes.overview: Tension starts to boil over in the mansion as alliances are formed and rivalries strengthen. Meanwhile, some of the Bachelorettes are starting to fall for the Honey Badger’s charms.

episodes.name: Episode 4
episodes.overview: A chemistry fuelled fly-fishing date sets one bachelorette apart as some cheeky flirtation and an honest conversation brings the two closer together.

episodes.name: Episode 5
episodes.overview: Sparks fly between Nick and one of the lucky bachelorettes that he picks for a fun and romantic speedboat date. Plus, surprise guests arrive for the group date.

episodes.name: Episode 6
episodes.overview: When Nick takes one lucky woman on a date, there is love in the air. Get ready for Romy’s bedtime visit on a camping trip with Nick. What is she getting up to?

episodes.name: Episode 7
episodes.overview: The intruders are here and, boy oh boy, they bring the drama. But the drama doesn’t stop there. Later at the cocktail party, the claws really come out, causing chaos and a runaway Bachelorette.

episodes.name: Episode 8
episodes.overview: The Bachelorettes compete for some alone time with Nick on a group date, and a single date announcement leaves one particular Bachelorette reeling.

episodes.name: Episode 9
episodes.overview: On a group date, the ladies participate in a lie detector test. What is Brooke’s big secret?

episodes.name: Episode 10
episodes.overview: With each rose ceremony and cocktail party, it gets harder and harder. If you thought being the Bachelor was easy, think again. Who will break the Honey Badger’s heart?

episodes.name: Episode 12
episodes.overview: Tension among the girls is brewing, with long-held resentment and jealousy running high.

episodes.name: Episode 13
episodes.overview: The girls go on a 1950s-inspired bowling date with Nick, who is hoping to sort out the hot strikes from the gutter balls. Emotions run high when the girls write a letter to their future self in 2028.

episodes.name: Episode 14
episodes.overview: It’s a hometown week like no other. Nick will answer some tough questions and meet the dad from hell. Later, tempers flare at an intense cocktail party.

episodes.name: Episode 15
episodes.overview: With feelings escalating and the final just around the corner, Nick needs to decide who he wants to meet his family. All three women lay their emotions on the line, but who will make it to the final?

episodes.name: Finale
episodes.overview: In this spectacular season finale, Nick’s incredible journey to love reaches its dramatic conclusion in tropical New Caledonia. Who will he choose to be with?

episodes.name: Episode 1
episodes.overview: Crack out the bubbly, lay out the cheeseboard and strap yourself in as 20 beautiful bachelorettes, battle a mix of excitement and nerves as they meet their Bachelor, astrophysicist Matt Agnew.

episodes.name: Episode 2
episodes.overview: The first single date sees one Bachelorette join Matt for a very special helicopter ride. Also eight hot new ladies have arrived looking for love and some are not willing to take the news lying down.

episodes.name: Episode 3
episodes.overview: There's tension in the mansion, a horse and carriage, a game of AFL, a cocktail party, a treasure hunt, a kiss (!) and one Bachelorette who runs out of the mansion in tears. Do not miss this episode!

episodes.name: Episode 4
episodes.overview:
This action-packed episode has everything from planes, to photo shoots and pashing.

One bachelorette is very vocal about her steamy encounter with the Bach, which rubs several girls the wrong way.

episodes.name: Episode 5
episodes.overview: Tensions are high after the last cocktail party, which saw someone play dirty for time with Matt. There’s a single date, an angry Bach, and a confrontation with one of the the bachelorettes

episodes.name: Episode 6
episodes.overview: Matt invites one of the girls to the Bach pad, where things move from cooking to romance. Later, a group date turns competitive and it’s clear one girl is rubbing the whole mansion the wrong way. Girl, bye!

episodes.name: Episode 7
episodes.overview: A single date card arrived and one lucky girl is whisked away blindfolded. During an intense cocktail party, two girls go head-to-head in a war of words and another is reduced to tears.

episodes.name: Episode 8
episodes.overview: One lucky girl gets a playful date with Matt where there's chemistry galore and massages! Matt's best mate arrives to meet some of the girls and the at the cocktail party Matt has a romantic pash!

episodes.name: Episode 9
episodes.overview: There's a private fire dance lesson with sparks and kisses. On the group date the girls are literally falling for Matt and at the cocktail party, one girl is gone before the rose ceremony even begins.

episodes.name: Episode 10
episodes.overview: Let's get physical! The adrenaline continues on tonight's epic episode. Matt has the girls doing acrobatics from a hanging cloth and repelling face down off a building.

episodes.name: Episode 11
episodes.overview: This episode welcomes a bunch of Bachelor and Bachelorette alumni to help Matt pick his dream woman. There's a single date involving chocolate and two girls go head-to-head at the cocktail party.

episodes.name: Episode 12
episodes.overview: A group date sees the girls draw their battle lines, as they scramble to get time with Matt. Later at an intense rose ceremony, a new rivalry in the house pushes one girl to absolute breaking point.

episodes.name: Episode 13
episodes.overview: In the group date the girls test their chemistry with Matt in front of each other. One lucky girl gets to "move in" with Matt. Later, two girls go head-to-head in an epic cocktail party showdown.

episodes.name: Episode 14
episodes.overview: It's Hometowns, and Matt travels around Australia to meet the nearest and dearest of the final four girls competing for his heart.

episodes.name: Episode 15
episodes.overview: To help him decide, Matt has planned an adventurous and romantic date with each girl. All three women lay their emotions on the line, but who will make it to the final rose ceremony?

episodes.name: Episode 16
episodes.overview: As the sun sets, the time has come for Matt to make one of the hardest decisions of his life. With emotions and hearts on the line, who will he choose to be with forever?

episodes.name: Episode 1
episodes.overview: The candles are lit, the cheeseboards are chilling, and the red carpet is ready. Locky Gilbert, our tall, dark and handsome Bachelor is about to meet a bevy of beauties who will take his breath away.

episodes.name: Episode 2
episodes.overview: First up is the single date Locky's been thinking about since the red carpet. Then it's the first group date where one bachelorette makes an impression so big it's felt throughout the mansion.

episodes.name: Episode 3
episodes.overview: After a surprise at the previous group date, the ladies are already feeling their feathers ruffled, and an impromptu cocktail party leaves the Bachelorettes questioning if they will secure a rose.

episodes.name: Episode 4
episodes.overview: One lucky Bachelorette gets extra time with Locky, but will it lead to unlocking his heart? The group date sees two teams go head-to-head, and a fierce rivalry between two Bachelorettes is uncovered.

episodes.name: Episode 5
episodes.overview: At another explosive cocktail party, drama has again erupted, setting the stage for more tears with one Bachelorette not sure who she can trust.

episodes.name: Episode 6
episodes.overview: What would a season of The Bachelor Australia be without a compatibility test! Will all the ladies play by the rules or will some fudge their answers to fall in line with Locky's?

episodes.name: Episode 7
episodes.overview: This week's group date goes ahead within the mansion compound, but it's what happens at the cocktail party that shakes the ladies to their core as relationship fractures begin to surface.

episodes.name: Episode 8
episodes.overview: With production at the mansion shutdown and the remaining Bachelorette's sent home, it's time to shake things up and get love back on track. Welcome to Love In Lockdown!

episodes.name: Episode 9
episodes.overview: As Love In Lockdown draws to a close, the girls are invited on a virtual group date where they will have the opportunity to introduce their nearest and dearest to Locky.

episodes.name: Episode 10
episodes.overview: Locky and the ladies return to the The Bachelor mansion and some things have changed dramatically. For some, deeper connections have been found, while for others initial sparks have fizzled out.

episodes.name: Episode 11
episodes.overview: It's the first group date since everyone returned to the mansion and the ladies finally get to do what they couldn't during lockdown - get physical with Locky! Locky is blindfolded and stripped down to his underwear.

episodes.name: Episode 12
episodes.overview: Only five women remain in the race for Locky's heart, and the pressure is on as he contemplates the difficult decision of who to take through to Hometowns.

episodes.name: Episode 13
episodes.overview: It's Hometowns and with four wildly different women offering four very distinct futures, Locky must face the firing line from the ladies families.

episodes.name: Episode 14
episodes.overview: Our Bachelor has fallen in love with two women and with the end in sight, it's going to be one unforgettable finale.

episodes.name: Episode 1
episodes.overview: Airline pilot, Jimmy Nicholson, is looking for love. While these vibrant, self-assured ladies may be sweet, they are not afraid to do what it takes to secure their first class ticket to love.

episodes.name: Episode 2
episodes.overview: Bachelor Jimmy takes a deserving bachelorette on a dreamy and fun-filled first date, where the sky truly is the limit. The very next day the infamous group date photo shoot is underway.

episodes.name: Episode 3
episodes.overview: Jimmy takes one lucky lady on a romantic single date. Sparks fly at the group date, Then the cocktail party begins smoothly, but when girl code is broken, tensions flare.

episodes.name: Episode 4
episodes.overview: It’s time for the most A-Mazing group date yet, as the girls need to navigate their way out to determine who is the most compatible with Jimmy, fighting their way for extra time with our bachelor.

episodes.name: Episode 5
episodes.overview: Jimmy and a very lucky lady soar to new heights. It's all smooth sailing until a mid-air emergency. A group date takes a scary turn and later, the girls go wild at the Cocktail Party!

episodes.name: Episode 6
episodes.overview: A compatibility test with a twist, sending one of the girls on a war path whilst of the group date. And later, a turn at the Cocktail Party will see someone leave the mansion for good.

episodes.name: Episode 7
episodes.overview: A family feast reignites the tension between two Bachelorette's, and Jimmy's family lay it all on the table. Then, the Cocktail Party, leads to an exit no one saw coming.

episodes.name: Episode 8
episodes.overview: Our Bachelor wants to test the limits of one lucky lady on a single date. Then, it's back to School for Jimmy and the Bachelorettes, but jealousy rages as the girl's jostle for Jimmy's attention.

episodes.name: Episode 9
episodes.overview: Jimmy's mum sits down with the bachelorettes for an eye-opening chat. Who will win her over, and who will fail to impress? The group date sees Jimmy take the ladies for a spot of glamping.

episodes.name: Episode 10
episodes.overview: Tonight, one bold bachelorette lays it on the line with Jimmy. At the group date, the women compete in the inaugural Bachelor Love Triathlon. Then, a bombshell is dropped at the cocktail party.

episodes.name: Episode 11
episodes.overview: Jimmy and the Bachelorettes come face a face-reading expert, who can determine how people face the world by their face structure. And later, an emotional rose ceremony, Jimmy sends two ladies home.

episodes.name: Episode 12
episodes.overview: Jimmy goes on a single date with each of the four remaining Bachelorettes, before being introduced to their nearest and dearest. Welcome to Hometowns.

episodes.name: Episode 13
episodes.overview: Jimmy's feelings have escalated for the remaining three women. With the finale around the corner, he can only choose two of these incredible women to meet his family.

episodes.name: Episode 14
episodes.overview: Jimmy shares a final date with each woman, before the pressure is turned up as he introduces them to his family. Then, the time has come for Jimmy to make one of the hardest decisions of his life.

episodes.name: Episode 1
episodes.overview: This year, for the first time ever, there is more than one Bachelor: Jed, Thomas and Felix. Our bachelors go on blind dates all around the country with 10 roses each to give out.

episodes.name: Episode 2
episodes.overview: It's the first night in the mansion and the Bachelorettes soon discover there's not 1, but 3 bachelors! Can Bad Bad Felix, Rock and Roll Drummer Jed and Italian Stallion Thomas find love, let's find out.

episodes.name: Episode 3
episodes.overview: Prepare yourself for one of the biggest drama-filled and most controversial episodes in Bachelor history!

episodes.name: Episode 4
episodes.overview: The mansion is reeling from the events of the night before: an explosive cocktail party and rose ceremony where Tash revealed to Jed (who passed it on to Felix) that Jess N has a boyfriend.

episodes.name: Episode 5
episodes.overview: Hold on to your hair extensions because a storm is brewing at the mansion. Following an eventful rose ceremony the night before, there is tension amongst the girls and 3 make a dramatic exit.

episodes.name: Episode 6
episodes.overview: Osher arrives to deliver the news that the boys have each invited three girls to a very special group date, where a loved one will be joining them at The Cali Beach Club.

episodes.name: Episode 7
episodes.overview: This episode picks up directly after the rose ceremony from the previous episode. Before Felix can say hello to half of his group, Tilly whisks Felix away for a private chat.

episodes.name: Episode 8
episodes.overview: Tash is back and Jed has a big decision to make. Is Tash the one that got away, or someone best left in the past? Thomas and Felix are concerned about the negative impact Tash's re-entry could have.

episodes.name: Episode 9
episodes.overview: The Bachelors are reminded we are near the end and they all reveal real feelings are developing rapidly. Each Bachelor will go on a single date and explore those connections further.

episodes.name: Episode 10
episodes.overview: It's the final single dates. All three bachelor's still have a lot of questions they need answered before they can commit to taking a girl to the finale.

episodes.name: Episode 11
episodes.overview: With the finale looming, the possibility of a proposal becomes very real for the bachelors and their remaining bachelorettes as they ultimately question if they have met The One.

episodes.name: Episode 12
episodes.overview: Jed, Felix and Thomas have decided who they want to face their happily ever after with.Three Bachelors, three engagement rings, two proposals. Settle in, it's going to be a night to remember.
